page.title: 05Interviews
page.content:
A local chartered accountant. A local chartered accountant told us that he lives in W Wickham and can walk to work at his rented office which is ten minutes from his home. He helps his clients with their money and travels all over the South of England doing his work, sometimes working very late. He employs two other people and uses three computers for keeping his clients rec- ords.He advertises in local newspapers. J Dagwell G Skinner L Mannal S Grayden.
A local School Teacher The local teacher was born in 1933 in Beckenham and she was educated at Marian Vian Primary School, Beckenham Girls Grammar School and Dartford Col- lege of Physical Education. She has taught for 19 years in Bromley. She has played Women's Cricket since 1948 for (cont.)
